data.description: Possible assumable VA Loan @3.5% 250K. Enjoy this renovated home central to downtown Arcadia.  Spend countless hours in your private pool.  The large double garage is ideal for a workshop, storage and parking your car.  The property has a great privacy fence.  Property is immaculate, and very well kept.  Security System with cameras add to the security of this property.  New roof installed in 2021.  Don't just be amazed at this home, get your best offer in now.
